@startuml Social_Sharing_Activity_Diagram

title Social Sharing Activity Diagram

|User|
start
:View Exhibit Information;
:Tap Share Button;
|System|
:Display Sharing Options;
|User|
:Add Personal Comment;
:Select Sharing Platform;
|System|
:Process Sharing Request;

if (Sharing Successful?) then (Yes)
  :Display Success Notification;
else (No)
  :Display Error Message;
endif
stop

@enduml

